      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick), over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>Filipino-style tocino sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until beginning to thicken</p>",
